    "description": "Eidai Kako Co.,Ltd. manufactures, imports, and sells resin sheets in Japan. It operates through two segments, Automotive Supplies-Related and Industrial Materials-Related. The company offers plastic profile extrusion molding products comprising interior and exterior components for electric appliances, interior and exterior materials for housing, interior and exterior components for office furniture, car floor mats, and bathtub covers, as well as AW mats and floor carpets. It also provides semiconductor-related parts, including stick magazines and storing IC devices and various electronic components; industrial parts that are used in the field of terminal block covers, LED lighting covers, aircraft parts, and escalator sliding parts; sewer pipe rehabilitation materials; and components for air conditioners, refrigerators, and washing machines and lighting fixtures for dryer stands, hoses, and refrigerator gaskets. The company also imports and exports its products. Eidai Kako Co.,Ltd. was founded in 1949 and is headquartered in Osaka, Japan."
